        <mxCell id="m2" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=13;align=center;" value="Cut into clips → Annotation-RD (10 rechecks per chunk, full duration) → agreement ≥ K&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;⇒ easy-theft set&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;clips of 10s with ss overlap=&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;30 simu × 1h ≈ 67k clips&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;non-detetced theft: dvr footage&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
